race.comment: BANORA BEACH (2) started big odds last time where he hit the ground running and was never headed, leading throughout to win by 0.8 lengths over 366, at Capalaba (19.60). Well placed and will be tough to beat. CAKE IS GREAT (7) is a well performed dog who recorded his 11th career win last time out at Q Straight (18.86). Strong form has emerged from his last run. Form should stack up. BECKY DUTTON (1) scored (30.96) last time out over 520m at Q Parklands 11 weeks ago. Solid record here including two wins. Will go close here with a clear run. MAXIMUS MALT (8) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.
